quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,Certainly the warnings did come to Pharaoh’s clan
  54,42,"who denied all of Our signs. So We seized them with the seizing of One [who is] all-mighty, Omnipotent"
  54,43,"Are your faithless better than those? Have you [been granted] [some sort of] immunity in the scriptures"
  54,44,"Do they say, ‘We are a confederate league’"
  54,45,"The league will be routed and turn its back [to flee]"
  54,46,"Indeed, the Hour is their tryst; and the Hour will be most calamitous and bitter"
  54,47,Indeed the guilty are steeped in error and madness
  54,48,"The day when they are dragged on their faces into the Fire, [it will be said to them,] ‘Taste the touch of hell!’"
  54,49,Indeed We have created everything in a measure
  54,50,"and Our command is but a single [word], like the twinkling of an eye"
  54,51,Certainly We have destroyed your likes. So is there anyone who will be admonished
  54,52,Everything they have done is in the books
  54,53,and everything big and small is committed to writing
  54,54,Indeed the Godwary will be amid gardens and streams
  54,55,in the abode of truthfulness with an omnipotent King